      • CONTENT_CHAT_URI

        public static final Uri CONTENT_CHAT_URI
        Content provider URI for chat messages of a given conversation. In case of single chat the conversation is identified by the contact phone number. In case of group chat the the conversation is identified by the unique chat ID.
